	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/08/07/morning-agenda-bank-of-americas-big-mortgage-settlement/" data-title="Morning Agenda: Bank of America&#8217;s Big Mortgage Settlement" data-description="Bank of America offered the U.S. the biggest settlement in history. | T-Mobile taunted Sprint after a takeover plan fell apart. | Why Walgreen shied away from an inversion in its deal for Alliance Boots. | Time Warner was silent on 21st Century Fox&#039;s takeover attempt during its earnings call on Wednesday.">
